🔷 Generate Token

```javascript id="u8k2p4"
const jwt = require("jsonwebtoken");

const token = jwt.sign(
  { userId: 1 },
  "secretKey",
  { expiresIn: "1h" }
);

console.log(token);
```

---

🔷 Verify Token

```javascript id="v4k9p2"
jwt.verify(token, "secretKey", (err, decoded) => {
  if (err) {
    console.log("Invalid token");
  } else {
    console.log(decoded);
  }
});
```

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

🔷 Authentication Flow

```text id="w2k8p4"
User Login
   ↓
Server verifies credentials
   ↓
JWT generated
   ↓
Client stores token
   ↓
Client sends token in request
   ↓
Server verifies token
   ↓
Access granted
```

---

🔷 Sending Token in Request

```text id="x8k2p4"
Authorization: Bearer <token>
```

