🔷 Best Practices for JWT

✔ Use strong secret key
✔ Set token expiry
✔ Store token securely
✔ Use HTTPS
✔ Do not store sensitive data in payload

---

⚠️ Common Mistakes

❌ Storing passwords in token
❌ No expiration time
❌ Weak secret key
❌ Not verifying token

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

🔷 JWT vs Sessions

| JWT              | Sessions         |
| ---------------- | ---------------- |
| Stateless        | Stateful         |
| Stored on client | Stored on server |
| Scalable         | Less scalable    |


